Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.78,0:00:23.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:26.88,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:30.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:33.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:48.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Working together, let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.73,0:00:55.95,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.95,0:01:02.91,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail-- let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.91,0:01:10.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:13.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey fraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:17.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most will be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:21.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.43,0:01:24.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:28.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:32.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:35.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.15,0:01:39.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:43.37,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up the pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:46.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:49.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.67,0:01:55.42,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag-- together, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:01:58.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you want with the Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get a new ship and\Nmove on to the seas ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, bye, Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you waver, who can we trust?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's vacate the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't come back... to this ship, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:47.45,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Severe Shock Hits the City\Nof Water! Iceberg Targeted!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was the first to find him?\NPlease let us question them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the culprit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they connected with the\Nannihilation of Franky House?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give us a statement!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:03:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell us the latest developments!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you hear about the incident\Nat the shipbuilding island?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that he died?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be Franky who did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This happened because they left him at large!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's also a strong chance it was\Ndone by pirates who visit the shipyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I heard that there was an\Nexplosion at the cape late last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that related to this incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but there are many pirates\Nwho got beaten up by the foremen, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is where you guys were...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We went to the trouble of getting a room\Nat this inn and yet no one's in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you all couldn't sleep, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.65,0:05:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you go, Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm... I kept a lookout at\Nthe rocky cape all night,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thinking that Robin-chan might come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where she went...\Nwithout saying anything to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been nothing but trouble\Nsince we got to this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had our money stolen, and moreover,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,look what happened with Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's badly wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he's running a fever\Nby now and can't even move!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm gonna wander around\Ntown looking for her today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we can find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I have specific\Nplaces in mind to check,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but in any case, it's certain that\Nshe's somewhere in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make this inn the place to\Nmeet up if something happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go look for her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible! The whole\Ntown is talking about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Last night, Iceberg-san\Nfrom the shipyard was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg-san was shot at his home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Was he killed?!\N--Well, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't someone who\Nmakes enemies of people!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a sec. Calm down, Paulie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:07:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Iceberg-san was found covered\Nin blood in his room this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still in a coma, so he's\Nunconscious right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, come to the\Nmain office immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lulu! Where's Paulie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just called him. He'll be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Newspaper reporters are already here\Nand it's quite an uproar outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...even though we're the ones who\Nwant to know what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although they tore up the whole office,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no trace of money\Nor valuables being stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it wasn't for robbery, who'd have\Na reason to shoot Iceberg-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.64,0:07:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, we're in big trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole town is in a panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something happens to him,\Nthe Galley-La Company--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as Water Seven-- will be finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor... How is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was shot twice from the front,\Nand thrice from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what happened in that room\Nlast night, but it sure was brutal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the forensics,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no trace of locks being\Npicked anywhere in the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The incident occurred in a\Nroom no one could've entered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing found in the room\Nwas a commonplace mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice pops was?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:08:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said that he's unconscious right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone thinks the world of him. Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that, Nami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who helped us yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the president of the shipbuilding\Ncompany and the mayor of Water Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like he's quite a big shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You couldn't come up with a\Nbigger incident than this in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go check.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Luffy! I'm coming, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's go look for Robin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait a little while and\Nsee how things turn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Extra edition! Extra! Extra!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water Seven's hero-- our mayor,\NIceberg-san-- fell victim to an assassin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:54.86,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mr. Iceberg Falls Victim to Assassin"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a news flash about the incident!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Iceberg-san okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible. How could this happen to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the culprit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The paper doesn't have any clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, paper guy! This doesn't have\Nthe crucial piece of information!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a vicious attack... It must be pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd sure like for us to catch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were pirates who went on a\Nrampage at Dock #1 yesterday, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mikazuki gang?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be shocking, but I think it\Nmight be the government's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.39,0:10:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lulu, what're you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about Corgy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each time he comes to talk to Iceberg-san,\Nhe gets turned down and goes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky must be the culprit after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what it was all about,\Nbut he must've done it out of spite.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't complain about the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone hears, you'll pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the goal of this unforgivable\Nculprit to gain wealth or power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:11:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this assassin who\Ndisappeared without a trace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:02.64,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mr. Iceberg Falls Victim to Assassin"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell did it?! I'm not\Ngonna let him get away with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for riding the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be arriving at Blue Station in\Nthe City of Water, Water Seven, soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Paulie-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paulie-san! Please give us\Na statement on the incident!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.78,0:12:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you told before you came here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up. Get out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What explanation did your company give you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give us a statement!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you deaf? I told you to get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hasn't there been any trouble that could have\Ncaused someone to target Mr. Iceberg's life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything that comes to your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any trouble with pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Paulie-san! Tell us...\N--I said get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dumbasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Hurry, Yagara!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Yagara-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, please get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's talking about Iceberg-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's true that he was attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Even if we go to the shipyard,\Nwe may not be able to see him like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's go to pops' house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said that his private residence\Nis inside the main office.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Because I'm weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That large amount of money... They stole it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.72,0:13:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't face everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were finally about to have Merry repaired...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiwi... Mozu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:15:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is, without a doubt,\Nthe place where Franky House was.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did this while I was gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... It must be them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you, Straw Hat Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you did this as retaliation for my\Nstealing your 200 million Berries?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you do this to\Nmy precious underlings?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How cold-blooded...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:16:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you guys are okay? Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had a terrible time.\NThose guys are really crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We want you to get revenge for us at any cost,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we've been spying on\Nthe Straw Hats' movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We saw them going into an inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From there, they headed to the\Nshipbuilding island a bit ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet they went to the place\Nthey went yesterday, Dock #1.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy... I'll crush you without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma! Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind is blowing like crazy! Hey, Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crazy wind! Crazy wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:17:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Crazy wind!\N--Don't romp around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a southern wind... Karock, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The waves are becoming quite rough, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.72,0:17:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As it stands, the sea train service\Nwill have to be stopped tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chimney! Gonbe! Get ready\Nto go back to the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aqua Laguna is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Water Seven\NWeather Forecasting Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:17:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An Aqua Laguna warning has just\Nbeen issued for the entire island.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its arrival time at Water Seven is\Nestimated to be after midnight tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah... It's that time of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.85,0:18:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was preoccupied with Iceberg-san's incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Aqua Laguna is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let those who didn't hear\Nthe warning yet know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No more working today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aqua Laguna?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that broadcast about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it about? Of course it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you a traveler?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you came here at a bad time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aqua Laguna is a storm surge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A storm surge, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Make sure you\Nevacuate to high ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This town will be submerged in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The town will be submerged...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It's not going\Nto happen right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the forecast, it'll be\Nhere around midnight tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this happens every year. Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be submerged in the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! This place will sink?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like it. At any rate,\Nlet's hurry and find Robin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where should we look?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... where would she be likely to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruins, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There probably aren't any here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anywhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what does she like?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.93,0:19:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That'd be ruins!\N--You keep saying that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then do you know what else she likes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking because I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.81,0:19:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't get in front of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that we don't know\Nanything about Robin-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell us something!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Iceberg-san!\N--What the hell happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.79,0:19:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't enter, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to see Ice pops sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, excuse me. Do you know where\Nthe entrance to the main office is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's no use. You go in through Dock #1,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but only concerned parties and\Ncertain reporters are allowed inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just you guys. Everyone is so\Nworried that they can't just sit and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all this fuss about?\NLots of people are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the bigger the audience, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.63,0:20:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! This rhythm is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.59,0:20:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...! Oh, no...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why at a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.93,0:20:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys! Did you just call my name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:20:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:20:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?! Where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! He's over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He's here!\N--Yow! Yow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yow! Yow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.62,0:21:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, don't be shy, ask me my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't wanna ask! Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who attacked\NIceberg-san, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?! He did it?!\N--It's gotta be him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be gone from this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.96,0:21:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be sent to the gallows, you punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... what noisy flies...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the No. 1 super guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The face of the Water Seven underworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! People call me... wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show yourself, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:23.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A piece of a dream that we started grasping
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.07,0:22:26.61,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing after something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.61,0:22:32.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We send our aspirations sailing into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.20,0:22:34.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we're exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.49,0:22:37.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a compass that can\Nsearch for something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.66,0:22:43.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you think we can keep it forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.09,0:22:46.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the dream\Nthat we will reach someday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:48.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to be adults as we\Nare now as much as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.97,0:22:51.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We pray to this endless sky that we look up at
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:54.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.85,0:22:57.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wild fantasies from our childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:23:00.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We trace unforgettable memories
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.48,0:23:06.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And try to keep the embers\Nburning that still consume us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.15,0:23:08.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To this familiar sunny sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.99,0:23:11.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Together we entrust our feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.78,0:23:14.37,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We go beyond the changing time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:19.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.09,0:23:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show yourself, Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.92,0:23:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that guy is Franky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.21,0:23:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you, bikini guy! I won't\Nbe happy until I beat you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.55,0:23:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it anymore.\NNo one can stop me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.89,0:23:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourself, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.51,0:23:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! What the hell?!\NHe breathed fire! That's kinda cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.48,0:23:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he's got Devil Fruit powers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.81,0:23:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.10,0:23:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Gum-Gum Human vs. Fire-breathing Cyborg"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.19,0:23:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
